Number one, notifications.

00:43:23.300 --> 00:43:25.660
I'm sure you're all
familiar with notifications.

00:43:25.870 --> 00:43:31.290
It looks something like this,
and it looks best when giants are on top.

00:43:32.780 --> 00:43:34.950
So you can get scoring alerts,
you can have alerts that pop up,

00:43:35.050 --> 00:43:40.100
they can have audio, they can also badge
the home screen icons.

00:43:40.180 --> 00:43:42.640
Well these have been massively popular.

00:43:42.640 --> 00:43:45.610
In fact,
we have already pushed more than a

00:43:45.800 --> 00:43:50.220
hundred billion push notifications.

00:43:50.310 --> 00:43:52.980
It's scaled beautifully.

00:43:53.300 --> 00:43:55.680
We've heard from our customers that
