00:43:55.730 --> 00:43:58.270
they'd like a better UI to get them.

00:43:58.270 --> 00:43:59.200
And we agree.

00:43:59.200 --> 00:44:03.200
And so we've built something that solves
some of the problems in the current one.

00:44:03.200 --> 00:44:07.200
Currently, when you get a notification,
it interrupts you.

00:44:07.200 --> 00:44:09.800
So if you're playing a game,
you get a modal alert,

00:44:09.900 --> 00:44:13.200
you have to deal with that modal
alert before you can go on.

00:44:13.200 --> 00:44:15.410
Also, in the lock screen,
you get this nice list of

00:44:15.410 --> 00:44:18.060
things that have happened
while your phone's been locked.

00:44:18.200 --> 00:44:21.200
But when you unlock it,
that list isn't persistent.

00:44:21.200 --> 00:44:25.200
There's no way to get back to that list
and go through those notifications.

00:44:25.200 --> 00:44:28.410
Well,
we have designed a solution that solves

00:44:28.490 --> 00:44:31.160
those issues and goes far beyond it.

00:44:31.280 --> 00:44:33.200
And we call it Notification Center.

00:44:33.200 --> 00:44:38.120
Notification Center is a single place.

00:44:38.760 --> 00:44:42.460
which combines together
all of your notifications.

00:44:42.500 --> 00:44:46.540
You can get to it at any time
from anywhere on your iPhone or

00:44:46.540 --> 00:44:50.530
iPad or iPod Touch just by swiping
your finger down from the top

00:44:50.660 --> 00:44:53.410
to reveal the notification center.

00:45:00.120 --> 00:45:02.260
So we think it is beautiful.

00:45:02.260 --> 00:45:07.090
It has your missed calls and voicemails,
text messages, mail messages,

00:45:07.170 --> 00:45:10.800
scoring alerts, Facebook updates,
any push notifications that come

00:45:10.800 --> 00:45:15.040
from the App Store all end up
right here in Notification Center.

00:45:15.040 --> 00:45:18.700
And we've even added stocks
and weather right up top.

00:45:19.360 --> 00:45:20.930
Now we didn't stop there.

00:45:20.930 --> 00:45:23.620
Notifications are no longer interrupting.

00:45:23.690 --> 00:45:27.920
So now if you're playing a game and
someone sends you say a text message,

00:45:27.920 --> 00:45:31.320
get a nice animation from the top,
it's right there.

00:45:35.910 --> 00:45:39.190
We can keep on playing your game and
it'll automatically dismiss itself.

00:45:39.190 --> 00:45:41.900
You could have just tapped on it
and it would take you to that app.

00:45:42.030 --> 00:45:44.500
But it doesn't matter because you can
always get back to it anytime just by

00:45:44.600 --> 00:45:47.300
swiping your finger down from the top.

00:45:47.410 --> 00:45:49.400
We've also improved the lock screen.

00:45:49.500 --> 00:45:53.490
You can see more information
for notifications here.

00:45:57.150 --> 00:46:00.940
And one of my favorite
features is for any one of the

