Dismiss it by swiping up.

00:46:40.630 --> 00:46:42.230
Really nice animation.

00:46:42.230 --> 00:46:46.650
You can see that we're still in
winter here in San Francisco.

00:46:47.680 --> 00:46:53.040
I get all of my messages here,
so text messages and scoring alerts.

00:46:53.140 --> 00:46:57.200
Down at the bottom here I have
