00:47:01.870 --> 00:47:04.000
If I see another notification
like the Facebook one,

00:47:04.180 --> 00:47:07.880
I tap on it,
takes me directly to the Facebook app.

00:47:07.980 --> 00:47:10.780
So it's really convenient,
and at any time again,

00:47:10.960 --> 00:47:14.530
swipe down from the top and you
get back to Notification Center.

00:47:14.850 --> 00:47:17.800
And that is Notification Center.

