Next is Safari.

00:52:10.900 --> 00:52:14.840
Safari is the best mobile
web browser out there.

00:52:14.910 --> 00:52:16.700
It's also the most popular.

00:52:16.700 --> 00:52:23.600
In fact, nearly two-thirds of all mobile
web browsing is done on Safari.

