00:52:28.850 --> 00:52:31.980
And it's the basis of all
web browsing on Android.

00:52:33.120 --> 00:52:37.690
So Safari Engine is the basis
of more than 90% of all web

00:52:37.740 --> 00:52:39.800
browsing on mobile devices.

00:52:39.880 --> 00:52:42.920
Well, in iOS 5,
we're making Safari even better.

00:52:43.030 --> 00:52:44.880
We've got some great features.

00:52:44.940 --> 00:52:47.390
The first is Reader.

00:52:47.690 --> 00:52:52.280
Safari Reader becomes available up
here as a new button when you're

00:52:52.280 --> 00:52:54.940
reading a story on a website.

00:52:54.960 --> 00:52:59.740
If you just tap on that button,
we take the story you're reading

00:52:59.750 --> 00:53:01.280
and make it front and center.

00:53:01.280 --> 00:53:04.920
We get rid of all the distractions,
set the font size right,

00:53:05.000 --> 00:53:09.750
and even if it's a multi-page story,
so you'd have to tap through multiple

00:53:09.750 --> 00:53:14.500
web pages normally to get to it,
we put it in a single scrolling story.

00:53:14.500 --> 00:53:16.780
It's really convenient.

00:53:23.270 --> 00:53:27.030
on top of that you can now
email the contents of the story

00:53:27.510 --> 00:53:31.320
before you could just email
the link but now when you email

00:53:31.450 --> 00:53:37.280
You get the link plus the
contents in your Compose window.

00:53:38.810 --> 00:53:41.740
And all of this works
really well on the iPad.

00:53:41.790 --> 00:53:44.410
It works great on the iPhone as well.

00:53:44.410 --> 00:53:45.700
It's the perfect size for it.

00:53:45.700 --> 00:53:47.460
It sets the font size right.

00:53:47.580 --> 00:53:49.140
It's really nice to read stories.

00:53:49.270 --> 00:53:50.100
So that's Safari Reader.

00:53:50.100 --> 00:53:53.740
The second one is Reading List.

00:53:55.410 --> 00:53:59.680
Reading list is a simple and
convenient way for you to quickly

00:53:59.680 --> 00:54:02.100
save a story to read it later.

00:54:02.180 --> 00:54:06.520
Just put it in the reading list and
when you add an item to reading list,

00:54:06.600 --> 00:54:09.330
it gets added to the reading
list on all of your iOS devices

00:54:09.900 --> 00:54:15.070
and even the reading list on
Safari on Mac and Safari on Windows.

00:54:20.030 --> 00:54:22.890
So if you don't have time to
finish it here on the iPad,

00:54:23.000 --> 00:54:26.580
you can finish reading
it later on your iPhone.

00:54:26.730 --> 00:54:29.660
And the next feature is tab browsing.

