01:55:39.180 --> 01:55:40.540
their pricing yet.

01:55:50.300 --> 01:55:52.840
Some of our customers won't
need this because they bought

01:55:52.840 --> 01:55:55.560
a lot of their music on iTunes,
but for those that do,

01:55:55.560 --> 01:56:00.600
it's an industry leading offering,
